      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      48.0,
      201.86,
      290.27,
      227.7
    ],
    "text": "1. This Act may be cited as the Betting and Gaming Levy (Amendment) Act, No. 25 of 2025.",
    "fonts": [
      "MinionPro-Bold",
      "MinionPro-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      48.0,
      239.46,
      290.28,
      277.3
    ],
    "text": "2. Section 2 of the Betting and Gaming Levy Act, No. 40 of 1988, as last amended by Act, No. 11 of 2023 is hereby further amended as follows: -",
    "fonts": [
      "MinionPro-Bold",
      "MinionPro-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.0,
      293.33,
      228.87,
      304.8
    ],
    "text": "(1) in subsection (1A) of that section -",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.0,
      320.53,
      290.52,
      359.2
    ],
    "text": "(a) in paragraph (b) of that subsection by the substitution for the words, \u201cten per centum; or\u201d of the words, \u201cten per centum;\u201d;",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Italic",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.0,
      374.93,
      290.51,
      481.6
    ],
    "text": "(b) in paragraph (c) of that subsection by the substitution for the words and figures, \u201cfor any year commencing on or after April 1, 2023, at the rate of fifteen per centum,\u201d of the words and figures, \u201cfor any year commencing on or after April 1, 2023 but ending prior to January 1, 2026 at the rate of fifteen per centum; or\u201d; and",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Italic",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.0,
      497.33,
      290.51,
      536.0
    ],
    "text": "(c) by the insertion immediately after paragraph (c) of that subsection of the following new paragraph: -",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Italic",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.8,
      77.0,
      244.25,
      90.14
    ],
    "text": "[Certified on 17th of December, 2025]",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
